## 🏗️ ARCHITECTURE - NEVER DEVIATE FROM THIS

### **Domain Architecture** (MEMORIZE THIS):
```
rensto.com          → Vercel (Next.js app - main site, marketplace, subscriptions, all public pages)
www.rensto.com      → Vercel (Next.js app - same as rensto.com)
admin.rensto.com    → Vercel (admin dashboard only)
api.rensto.com      → Vercel (API endpoints - redundant with rensto.com/api/* but works)
portal.rensto.com   → Vercel (customer portals - planned)
```

### **Critical Rules**:
1. ✅ **rensto.com is on Vercel** - Next.js app (`apps/web/rensto-site/`)
2. ✅ **API routes available at**: `rensto.com/api/*` AND `api.rensto.com/api/*` (both work)
3. ✅ **ALWAYS** read brain.md first (Mission Control), then CLAUDE.md before architectural decisions
4. ✅ **Reference conflicts**: Query NotebookLM 5811a372 for hierarchy and cross-reference map
5. ⚠️ **Webflow**: Retired. All pages served by Next.js (rensto-site) on Vercel.

