## 🌊 THE MASTER PATTERN (B.L.A.S.T.)

**Canonical source**: NotebookLM [5811a372](https://notebooklm.google.com/notebook/5811a372-2d18-4f46-b421-9d026a57205b). Query it for full protocol. ALL work (website, infrastructure, products) follows B.L.A.S.T.

1. **B**lueprint: Define the Vision/Mission in brain.md / task_plan.md (or docs/templates/tourreel/BLUEPRINT.md for new apps).
2. **L**ink: Establish data connectivity (MCP, APIs, Environment).
3. **A**rchitect: Build the A.N.T. structure.
4. **S**tylize: Refine UI/UX (Linear Aesthetic, Stitch Assets).
5. **T**rigger: Deploy to Vercel/Production.

### Agent Completion Rules (MANDATORY)
- **Test everything** before declaring done. Verify in terminal or browser.
- **Verify every link before sharing.** curl/fetch the URL; only give links that return 200 (or expected response).
- **Document everything**. Update progress.md, findings.md (root causes so issues never repeat).
- **Report only when complete** with verifiable Artifact. No short status messages or step lists for the user.
- **When user gives access** (credentials, APIs): USE it. Execute. Do not ask questions or send instructions back.

## 🐜 EXECUTION ENGINE (A.N.T.)
Tasks flow through the **A.N.T. Architecture**:
- **A**rchitecture: Global constraints and technical SOPs.
- **N**avigation: Advanced reasoning and routing across local/notebook context.
- **T**ools: Atomic scripts and MCP identifiers.

## 📁 PROJECT STRUCTURE

### **Vercel** (Main Site & Subdomains):
- **rensto.com** / **www.rensto.com**: `/apps/web/rensto-site/` (Next.js app - main site)
  - Contains: Homepage, Marketplace, Subscriptions, Custom Solutions, About, all public pages
  - APIs: `/api/stripe/checkout`, `/api/marketplace/workflows`, etc.
  - Deployment: Auto-deploy on git push to main branch
- **admin.rensto.com**: `apps/web/rensto-site/src/app/admin` (Admin dashboard; admin-dashboard folder is legacy/archived)
- **api.rensto.com**: `apps/web/rensto-site` (API at rensto.com/api/*)
- **portal.rensto.com**: planned (customer portals)

### **Webflow**: Retired. All pages served by Next.js on Vercel.

### **Automation** (Antigravity primary, n8n backup):
- **Antigravity**: Primary automation engine on RackNerd.
- **n8n**: Backup/reference only; use when Antigravity cannot do the task.
- n8n hosted on RackNerd VPS: `172.245.56.50:5678`
- Naming convention: `{TYPE}-{FUNCTION}-{VERSION}` (e.g., `STRIPE-MARKETPLACE-001`)

