## 🚨 CRITICAL MISTAKES TO AVOID

### **Architecture Mistakes**:
1. ❌ Changing rensto.com DNS without approval (currently on Vercel)
2. ❌ Creating API routes in wrong location (should be in `apps/web/rensto-site/src/app/api/`)
3. ❌ Not following domain separation (admin vs main site vs APIs)
4. ❌ Assuming Webflow is active (it's archived - DNS doesn't point to it)

### **Code Mistakes**:
1. ❌ Missing React import in Next.js files
2. ❌ Forgetting to add dependencies to package.json
3. ❌ Not setting environment variables in all environments

### **Documentation Mistakes**:
1. ❌ Not updating CLAUDE.md after major changes
2. ❌ Creating duplicate documentation
3. ❌ Not archiving outdated docs

