## 🎯 QUICK DECISION TREE

### "Where should this code go?"
- Public website content? → **Vercel rensto.com** (`/apps/web/rensto-site/src/app/`)
- API endpoint? → **Vercel rensto.com/api** (`/apps/web/rensto-site/src/app/api/`)
- Admin dashboard? → **Vercel admin.rensto.com** (`/apps/web/rensto-site/src/app/admin`)
- Customer portal? → **Vercel portal.rensto.com** (`/live-systems/customer-portal/`)
- Workflow automation? → **Antigravity** (primary on RackNerd); **n8n** (backup only)

### "Which database should I use?"
- App/customer data? → **PostgreSQL** (primary)
- Cache/sessions/queues? → **Redis**
- Dashboards/config? → **Aitable.ai** (in use)
- Documentation? → **Notion** (high-level only)
- >50K records? → **MongoDB** (customer projects only)
- Real-time app? → **Supabase** (customer projects only)

